msgid "Telegram Desktop Accessibility"
msgstr "Telegram 電腦版無障礙支援"

msgid ""
"Improves Telegram Desktop accessibility for NVDA users.\n"
"\n"
"This release fixes chat list focus announcements when Telegram exposes a broken UIA selection container, and applies the same protection to the phone number country selection dialog."
msgstr ""
"改善 Telegram 電腦版與 NVDA 搭配使用時的無障礙體驗。\n"
"\n"
"此版本修正 Telegram 暴露損壞的 UIA 選取容器時，聊天室清單焦點提示無法正常朗讀的問題，並將同樣的保護套用到電話號碼國家/地區選擇對話框。"

msgid "Fixed chat list item focus speech in Telegram Desktop 6.8.x by avoiding a failing UIA selection container query."
msgstr "透過避開失敗的 UIA 選取容器查詢，修正 Telegram 電腦版 6.8.x 中聊天室清單項目的焦點朗讀。"
